 Q.   Martin Kaymer told us two hours ago that there is a big question among golf pros, talking about football, and especially Germany versus Spain, which could collide in the final.   
SERGIO GARCÃA:   Yeah, it could happen.   I think Spain needs to start playing a little bit better than they have.   The first three games, or at least the first and third game.   
